Streetname Identifier. Foreign key to STNAME table. For City of Seattle ROW, association of specific alias StreetName with Segment performed by SDOT.

Use Alias in Geocode Flag.Flag to identify suitability to use Alias Streetname record with feature class attributes as part of Geocoding index creation. Suitability of associated Address range with Alias Streetname determined by Historical usage, or DCLU Address establishment process. Assignment to record performed by SND.
